{"tid":1289030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】我要問77遊行發起人VN，究竟你既遊行主題係乜？點解咁多牛鬼蛇神妖魔鬼怪出晒黎騎劫","createTime":"2019-07-06T01:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T02:42:59.000Z","uid":263585,"like":19,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53451956626544df2b10546299ee4a05e77d0cf8","tid":1289030,"uid":263585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNzTG1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNzTG1k.jpg&h=9b2440fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點啊?點解咁撚多其他奇怪野架?遊行主題唔係五大訴求咩?<br />\n香港人先搞掂香港事。<br />\n如果俾呢D奇怪野加入黎，騎劫晒成事，會令到個遊行好膠。<br />\nVN你究竟咩睇法?<br />\n如果有呢D怪雞野，講真我一定唔去，亦一定叫朋友唔好去。<br />\n可唔可以澄清下，唔好俾呢D人黎呃光環、騎劫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SocialistAction/photos/a.156508364361365/2526534390692072/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSocialistAction%2Fphotos%2Fa.156508364361365%2F2526534390692072%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=f6302011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SocialistAction/photos/a.156508364361365/2526534390692072/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"951ddb36ec4afb2188f19bf426f25881a1709c79","tid":1289030,"uid":263585,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"推，真心問，好怕呢D建設民主中國觀念"},{"pid":"466725892cbdedeaa4e25935f2adecd8b1d06f01","tid":1289030,"uid":263585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"推推，究竟呢個咩社會主義行動係咩家伙黎架"},{"pid":"f14a39ba557c59988fd0dd5941287866cc8a799a","tid":1289030,"uid":21887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:08:14.000Z","msg":"[7.7九龍遊行] 我會盡力完成一場和理非遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1288763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1288763</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nVL講得好清楚啦 <br />\n自己睇<br />\n<br />\n<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要去醫院驗傷  我唔會解鎖電話 我唔會簽任何文件</code>"},{"pid":"96cbd39d5edf234c385c9412de474e2a86f04cce","tid":1289030,"uid":263585,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:10:17.000Z","msg":"自推....<br />\nVN你咁辛苦申請不反對通知書，你都唔想個遊行人少少咁架?<br />\n講真，如果唔係對焦香港的事，真冇興趣去。<br />\n如果非你原意，一定要澄清返，同埋要去佢個FB到叫佢唔好改主題，騎劫"},{"pid":"a742e8b732454b47c25be10c746ff8962500a075","tid":1289030,"uid":90521,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"466725892cbdedeaa4e25935f2adecd8b1d06f01","tid":1289030,"uid":263585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"推推，究竟呢個咩社會主義行動係咩家伙黎架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:11:28.000Z","msg":"社會主義行動以d左膠常客都唔識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩鳩都走出黎抽水既組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中東戰爭佢地都抽水賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68602647f7773587416e87709d004548c6f8a9d0","tid":1289030,"uid":263585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14a39ba557c59988fd0dd5941287866cc8a799a","tid":1289030,"uid":21887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:08:14.000Z","msg":"[7.7九龍遊行] 我會盡力完成一場和理非遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1288763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1288763</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nVL講得好清楚啦 <br />\n自己睇<br />\n<br />\n<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要去醫院驗傷  我唔會解鎖電話 我唔會簽任何文件</code>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:12:55.000Z","msg":"我有睇VN呢個POST。<br />\n但呢個咩社會主義行動，咁樣騎劫晒成件事，你覺得冇問題?"},{"pid":"b0ffdb866a56b2ede7da752d38f41e37879be6d2","tid":1289030,"uid":238560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68602647f7773587416e87709d004548c6f8a9d0","tid":1289030,"uid":263585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14a39ba557c59988fd0dd5941287866cc8a799a","tid":1289030,"uid":21887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:08:14.000Z","msg":"[7.7九龍遊行] 我會盡力完成一場和理非遊行<br />\n<a href=\"http